setTempletOfFeed

void setTempletOfFeed(com.sun.syndication.feed.synd.SyndFeed templetOfFeed)
setup templetOfFeed for Builder.buildFeed() and Fetcher.fetchFeeds() User can new SyndFeed() and then call setSyndFeed(SyndFeed templetFeed). But this way is not commended, in our advice, it's much better to dynamically configure the necessary parameter template in IOC container

参数：
templetFeed -
